Q.1 Explain why data structures and algorithms are essential in handling large inventories.

ANS :

We use data Structures and algorithms for handling large inventories because they determine how 
quickly and effectively data can be stored,accessed and manipulated.
As we are dealing with large amount of data ,thus it makes it easy for us by using appropriate data 
structures we can improve the performance of operations like adding ,updating and deleting products.



